Note:
aott/analysis/hotpath_analysis/cold_path_optimizer.runa
Cold Path Optimization Module for AOTT Code Layout

This module provides cold path optimization for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Cold code identification and marking
- Code layout optimization for cache performance
- Cold path outlining and separation
- Exception path optimization
- Unlikely branch prediction hints
- Cold code compression
- Dead code elimination in cold paths
- Cold path register allocation
- Memory layout optimization
- Cold path instrumentation removal
- Profile-guided cold path optimization
- Cross-function cold path analysis
- Cold path debugging support
- Size optimization for cold code
- Cold path execution monitoring
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

